<!-- PROJECT -->
<section class="sec" id="project">
  <p class="sec-label">Course-Related Work</p>
  <h2 class="sec-title">Scientific Investigation</h2>
  <div class="divider"></div>

  <div class="project-card">
    <h3>Defending Your Dermis</h3>
    <p class="project-sub">A Comparative Study of Organic and Synthetic Sunscreens</p>

    <!-- PROJECT PHOTO -->
    <div class="photo-placeholder">
      <div class="ph-icon">🔬</div>
      <p>[Photo: Sunscreen Research Project / Research Poster]</p>
      <small>Upload as: images/sunscreen-project.jpg</small>
    </div>

    <p>Our project investigated the effectiveness of commercial and homemade sunscreens in protecting against UV radiation — a major risk factor for skin damage and skin cancer. Over several months, my team compared different sunscreen formulations under Singapore's high UV conditions and analysed their UV Protection Rating (UV PR) using UV indicator cards.</p>
    <p>This project allowed me to experience the complete scientific research process — from designing experiments and collecting data to analysing results and presenting evidence-based conclusions to teachers and judges.</p>

    <h4 style="color:var(--navy);font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:10px;">My Contributions</h4>
    <ul class="contrib-list">
      <li>Planned and discussed experimental design with my team</li>
      <li>Applied sunscreen samples consistently to ensure fair testing</li>
      <li>Recorded UV Protection Rating (UV PR) results during each trial</li>
      <li>Collected and organised experimental data over multiple weeks</li>
      <li>Compared commercial and homemade sunscreen formulations</li>
      <li>Analysed patterns in the results and contributed to findings</li>
      <li>Assisted in preparing and designing the final research poster</li>
      <li>Presented findings clearly to teachers and judges</li>
    </ul>

    <h4 style="color:var(--navy);font-size:.9rem;font-weight:700;margin:16px 0 12px;">Scientific Skills Developed</h4>
    <div class="skills-row">
      <div class="skill-box">
        <h4>🧪 Experimental Design</h4>
        <p>Controlled variables precisely — equal sunscreen amounts, water volume, identical UV cards and consistent testing durations — ensuring only the formulation changed.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-box">
        <h4>📊 Data Collection & Analysis</h4>
        <p>Conducted multiple experiments across different weeks and calculated averages — learning that scientific conclusions require repeated observations, not assumptions.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-box">
        <h4>🧠 Critical Thinking</h4>
        <p>When homemade sunscreen underperformed, analysed possible reasons including uneven application and formulation differences rather than simply concluding it "failed."</p>
      </div>
      <div class="skill-box">
        <h4>🤝 Teamwork</h4>
        <p>Divided responsibilities, discussed improvements after each experiment, and supported one another throughout the investigation.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

